title: BSkyB Falls the Shadow The Life and Times of Athol Fugard PDTV x
description:
Falls the Shadow: The Life and Times of Athol Fugard

Arts Documentary hosted by Tony Palmer, published by BSkyB in 2012 - English narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/1/19/Falls-the-Shadow-The-Life-and-Times-of-Athol-Fugard-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
To mark the 80th birthday of South African playwright Athol Fugard, this special film by Tony Palmer explores the writer's fascinating past and diverse influences.
